    "data": [
        {
            "title": "壁球｜亞青賽今日煞科 港女隊下午3時與大馬爭標",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"港女隊殺入亞青賽決賽。壁總圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a786a7bdf2b7afdc295a834562a435be/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250216/_2025021609304724854.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">港女隊殺入亞青賽決賽。壁總圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>亞洲青少年壁球團體錦標賽昨日上演4強階段，梁加萱、鄺恩琳、張芷晴及鄧凱琳組成的女隊面對印度，以場數2:1氣走對手，晉級今日決賽，下午3時與馬來西亞爭標。男子港隊方面在昨日過關，今晨10時與日本爭奪第5名，煞科日賽事繼續在香港壁球中心上演。 男子組決賽於12時30分上演，由南韓與大馬競逐冠軍。\n\n</p>\n<p>決賽日賽事，繼續在港台電視32台直播：\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://app7.rthk.hk/special/sports32/22ndasiayoungsquash/\">https://app7.rthk.hk/special/sports32/22ndasiayoungsquash/</a>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女隊殺入亞青賽決賽。壁總圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43ad87d3752fd2198dd69828c96d7a1c/2025-02/SQ_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女隊殺入亞青賽決賽。壁總圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女隊殺入亞青賽決賽。壁總圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec083d75809ff644fdaef57be5697454/2025-02/SQ_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女隊殺入亞青賽決賽。壁總圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053051/即時-體育-壁球-亞青賽今日煞科-港女隊下午3時與大馬爭標",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-16 09:41:32",
